==English==
===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''isomorphism'''
#{{biology}} the [[similarity]] in [[form]] of [[organism]]s of different [[ancestry]]
#{{mathematics}} a [[one-to-one]] [[correspondence]] between all the [[element]]s of two [[set]]s such that any [[operation]] returns the same [[result]] on either set; a [[function]] that [[map]]s one of these sets to the other
#{{chemistry}} the similarity in the [[crystal]] structures of similar [[chemical]] [[compound]]s
#(''sociology'') the similarity in the structure or [[processes]] of different [[organization]]s
